# Project Directory Structure

This file serves as a reminder that all commands should be run from:
/app/

NOT from the root directory.

## Common Commands:
- npm run dev     # Run from /app/ directory
- npm run build   # Run from /app/ directory
- npx astro ...   # Run from /app/ directory

## Project Structure
/controlpanel          # Root directory
  /app                 # Astro project directory (RUN COMMANDS HERE)
    /src               # Source files 
    package.json       # Dependencies
    astro.config.mjs   # Astro configuration
  /prototype           # Original prototype (reference only) 